title: Rob Liefeld vorrebbe rivedere Ryan Reynolds nei panni di Lanterna Verde
body:
Rob Liefeld vorrebbe rivedere Ryan Reynolds nei panni di Lanterna Verde

Il creatore di Deadpool, Rob Liefeld, ha rivelato che gli piacerebbe vedere Ryan Reynolds riprendere il ruolo in un prossimo film di Green Lantern.

Prima che si facesse conoscere con il nome di Mercenario Chiacchierone, l’attore ha prima tentato di mettere in risalto un altro franchise di supereroi interpretando il personaggio della DC Comics. Sfortunatamente, a differenza del suo periodo…

summary: cant believe i wasted so many years of my life thinking the fantastic four were boring??? i somewhat remember watching the...
body: cant believe i wasted so many years of my life thinking the fantastic four were boring??? i somewhat remember watching the (2005) movie and midly liking it as a kid but that was about it - but now i’m reading the first issue and i’m actually having a blast! i’m not even a big comic reader (especially the old ones) nor was a big fan of de F.F but i’m having a lot of fun rn… i probably won’t be done with the 1961 comic in a while but does anyone knows what i should read next? what are others, more recent issues featuring them good to read?
